{"tid":2258003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做業主都有得屌鳩保安 係香港做納稅人 政府管理不善 屌鳩佢原來犯法","createTime":"2020-10-25T16:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T02:22:15.000Z","uid":98915,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c201e0f103244d9c59538a43369e8dd297ecbf","tid":2258003,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"你話香港幾撚荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地就全香港人嘅 稅又係我哋交嘅<br />\n<br />\n但地呢 就港共攞去賤價賣嘅<br />\n福利就俾公墓猿同腥移民嘅<br />\n錢就港共袋嘅 炒價就我哋食嘅<br />\n<br />\n上街屌佢老母 舉吓牌<br />\n仲要俾佢揼足一年 話你冇資格冇權力<br />\n<br />\n最後繼續困係個臭坑日日返工不了<br />\n仲得閒可以批鬥吓其他監躉<br />\n好幸福 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446eee5ae78b8c07327e2aa2aaf64f973106780b","tid":2258003,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T18:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901e7b902f109d14c8f5bf56ed8c5d0115cb0992","tid":2258003,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}